var e=[{id:`L2_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`<color=#ffd34c>관리국 재건 도시 군 사령부의 지원 요청입니다.</color>`,JPN:`<color=#ffd34c>管理局再建都市軍司令部の支援要請です。</color>`,ENG:`<color=#ffd34c>A support request has arrived from the Administration Rebuilt City Military Headquarters.</color>`,TWN:`<color=#ffd34c>來自管理局重建城市軍司令部的支援請求。</color>`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L3_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`마젤란 예언회로 추정되는 무리들이 도시를 습격했습니다.`,JPN:`マジェラン預言会と推定される集団が都市を襲撃してきました。`,ENG:`Groups that are assumed to be with the Magellan's Prediction Society have raided the city.`,TWN:`疑似為麥哲倫預言會的一群人突擊了城市。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L4_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`1차 공세는 막았지만 이는 일시적인 눈속임이더군요.`,JPN:`先陣は食い止めましたが、それは一時的な誤魔化しにすぎませんでした。`,ENG:`Although the first wave of attacks were stopped, it was part of their deceptive tactics.`,TWN:`雖然擋下了他們的第一波攻擊，但這只是他們一時的障眼法。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L5_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`내부 공작으로 대공방어가 무력화되는 바람에 사교도 측 함선들이 도시 공역을 점령한 상황입니다.`,JPN:`内部工作により対空防御が無力化したため、
邪教徒側の艦船が都市の空域を占領している状況です。`,ENG:`Our anti-air defenses were shut down due to their inside job, which allowed the cultist ships to seize our city's air space.`,TWN:`由於內部作業讓防空機制處於無效化狀態，所以目前異教徒的艦船佔領了城市的空域。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L6_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`사교도가 사단 규모의 전력을 숨기고 있었다는 사실을 알아차리지 못한 건 저희의 실책입니다.`,JPN:`邪教徒が師団規模の戦力を隠していたことに
気付かなかったのは、我々の失策です。`,ENG:`It was our mistake for not realizing that the cultists were hiding an entire division.`,TWN:`沒能及時發現異教徒隱藏了真正實力是我們的失策。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L7_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`현 상황을 타개하기 위해선 태스크포스 여러분들의 도움이 절실히 필요합니다.`,JPN:`現状を打開するためには、是非ともタスクフォースの皆様の力が必要です。`,ENG:`We are in desperate need of help from everyone at the TASKFORCE to overcome this situation.`,TWN:`為了打破現在的困境，我們迫切需要各位特遣勢力公司的幫助。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L8_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`여러분의 안전한 공역 진입을 위해, 적들을 최대한 교란하고 있겠습니다.`,JPN:`皆様の安全な空域進入のために、敵を最大限撹乱しています。`,ENG:`We will do our best to disrupt their defenses in order to allow your safe entry to our air space.`,TWN:`為了能讓你們安全地進入空域，我們正在盡最大的努力擾亂敵人。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`THEMA_COFFIN_FULL`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}}];export{e as default};